{"tid":1977861,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"史丹福調查要人呀!!!","createTime":"2020-04-18T09:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T07:15:28.000Z","uid":63821,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"614f020ca71b451a7f963266b3a37598f8ea9581","tid":1977861,"uid":63821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺一個臺灣教授fb見到。<br />\n有另一個臺灣人喺Standford醫學院做教授，調查緊武漢肺炎嘅Community response（即係個人衛生習慣、對於疾病嘅awareness嗰啲）<br />\n<br />\n香港係其中一個重點研究國家。墨西哥已經有2萬幾人回覆咗，臺灣而家上緊去。<br />\n<br />\n條link喺呢度，唔識睇英文可以喺右上角轉正體中文。<br />\n<a href=\"https://stanforduniversity.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_6tlTxkYSZMlExJH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstanforduniversity.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_6tlTxkYSZMlExJH&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=91452b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://stanforduniversity.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_6tlTxkYSZMlExJH</a><br />\n<br />\n大家用5分鐘就可以架啦，越多人回應，啲數據就越有意義，等國際睇到香港人（唔撚係個政府）幾高質。或者至少喺呢啲國際研究入面可以霸個靚位。<br />\n<br />\n今次香港人自救其實好犀利，但係國際社會真係睇少咗香港呢個特別嘅例子（諗起黃任匡琴日個post......）<br />\nAnyways，希望大家可以一齊幫手推呢個研究出去。"},{"pid":"1a3d75fdeae54a6b691e2fd4ff7d8d9bf4daff46","tid":1977861,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3b85942d0d306f4856d0b7b617b36a4459663c","tid":1977861,"uid":63821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"4月20號就完架啦！！！！快啲入去填！！！"},{"pid":"f7d0d96ce56ede2d5db173dc7b4693a438691116","tid":1977861,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"Up<br />\n已填"},{"pid":"cbb02815c724ded914ca6c911fa65ffe7e8fc9c7","tid":1977861,"uid":146243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"done"},{"pid":"99e35f25b1e72a62563c8ed3f8720473b4770eb1","tid":1977861,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy